Bon Iver's Justin Vernon shares thoughts on facing anxiety
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

During an interview with Jill Riley in The Current studio, Justin Vernon of Bon Iver shares his thoughts about anxiety — and ways to support oneself and others in facing it. 

Watch the full interview here: https://youtu.be/IJtIZgslmqU
